                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170521-49-off253 t18170521-49-cd254"></join>, one coat, value 2l.; two handkerchiefs, value 7s.; and one pair of spectacles, value 1l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18170521-49-victim367" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
